To build a core version of dvda-author-@VERSION@, use the autotools with following command line: 

./configure --enable-core-build 

or add the following symbolic constants either to CPPFLAGS (using -DWITHOUT_...) or to hard code in commonvars.h:
WITHOUT_FLAC
WITHOUT_OGG
WITHOUT_FIXWAV
WITHOUT_SOX
WITHOUT_DVDAUTHOR
HAVE_CORE_BUILD

